    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Party Slime Time is an online party game to enjoy with your friends, explore a variety of different game boards and participate in 70 minigames!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore The Boards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867460/extras/3efd06f273b4d1dcc9b77cb82dcf5d35.avif?t=1763978426\" alt=\"A screenshot of Party Slime Time showcasing the board Oriental Palace\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whilst on the board game sections you can earn artefact shards which are used to purchase artefacts which are the key to winning the game, along with collecting slime pieces which can be used to increase your movement or do decrease an opponents movement. Choose when to use the slime wisely!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle Through The Minigames</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867460/extras/9c9ed7b34afbacad65861b40b0b5b9c8.avif?t=1763978426\" alt=\"A screenshot of Party Slime Time showcasing the mini game Team Football \" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on a variety of different minigames after each turn to earn additional artefact shards, these can vary between platformer stages, sports, button mashing and guessing games, to name a few types!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These take the form of free for all, team and uneven team minigames.</p>",
